Let's get you back to sleep.
We've got a long flight tomorrow.

41
00:08:06,953 --> 00:08:11,185
Here, put Charlie in charge. You
won't have more nightmares tonight.

42
00:08:12,992 --> 00:08:14,823
Good night.

43
