82
00:13:26,939 --> 00:13:29,430
8 a.m. in the lobby,
with references.

83
00:13:30,309 --> 00:13:32,800
- Okay, thanks.
- Sylvia didn't forget.

84
00:13:33,813 --> 00:13:35,405
Sylvia never forgets.

85
