Dad, we don't need a nanny.

86
00:13:40,085 --> 00:13:43,054
We can talk about later.
Come on, let's get you to bed.

87
00:13:43,422 --> 00:13:46,448
- But I'm not tired.
- But we got a big day tomorrow...

88
00:13:46,659 --> 00:13:51,961
